WEBVTT

00:10.100 --> 00:11.450
但是不肯给我
but she wouldn't let me keep them.

00:12.620 --> 00:13.500
好吧
All right.

00:13.510 --> 00:15.030
我要知道这个人是谁
I want to know who this guy is.

00:15.060 --> 00:16.640
他说他叫苏林斯
Said his name was Sullins.

00:17.560 --> 00:19.570
阿历克斯感谢你过来
Alex, thanks for coming in.

00:20.500 --> 00:21.500
你好兰
Hello, Lang.

00:21.510 --> 00:23.470
怎么回事? 有许多警察
What's going on? There's all kinds

00:23.480 --> 00:25.280
在搜查你的办公室
of suits over here going through your office.

00:25.450 --> 00:26.670
我认识你是吗
I know you, huh?

00:26.960 --> 00:27.260
恐怕认错了
Afraid not.

00:27.270 --> 00:28.440
不 没有
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:29.030 --> 00:30.230
你是麦克法登
You're McFadden.

00:30.250 --> 00:31.390
你把我和别人搞混了
You've confused me with someone else.

00:31.400 --> 00:32.970
应该是在大使那儿
You were with the ambassador.

00:33.020 --> 00:35.160
你不了解我 我也不了解你
You don't know me, I don't know you,

00:35.170 --> 00:36.950
不过你的任务是把我弄出去
but it's your job to get me out of here.

00:36.960 --> 00:38.370
-你们明天就越狱 -下午三点
You break out tomorrow. By 3:00 p.m.

00:38.380 --> 00:40.160
-你是说凌晨吧 -不 是下午
You mean a.m. No, I mean p.m.

00:40.170 --> 00:42.640
我们明天就动手 就在大白天
We're doing this tomorrow in the middle of the day.

00:51.180 --> 00:52.310
把戒指给我
Give me the ring.

00:53.820 --> 00:55.170
算你聪明
Wise decision.

00:59.500 --> 01:00.670
戒指要吗 兄弟?
Want the rin brother?

01:00.870 --> 01:02.450
这可不是我的作风 伙计
That's more your style, man.

01:12.400 --> 01:14.110
没关系 没关系的
It's all right, it's all right.

01:17.200 --> 01:18.980
你们都退开 退开
You all go on back. Go ahead.

01:19.790 --> 01:20.870
别 快退开
No, go ahead.

01:23.730 --> 01:24.900
小意思
A word.

01:30.360 --> 01:32.430
你以后要更小心一点
You should try and be more careful in the future.

01:32.460 --> 01:33.590
是 先生
Yes, sir.

01:57.700 --> 01:58.740
你叫什么?
What's your name?

02:00.610 --> 02:01.690
帝格
Tyge.

02:01.940 --> 02:03.050
迈克
Michael.

02:03.570 --> 02:04.650
那个澳洲人
The Australian.

02:04.660 --> 02:06.190
你说你是在尼斯认识他的
You said you knew him from Nice.

02:06.400 --> 02:07.480
是真的吗
Is that true?

02:07.690 --> 02:09.000
你在说我是个骗子?
You calling me a liar now?

02:09.010 --> 02:10.430
他说你满口谎话
He says you're full of it.

02:10.820 --> 02:12.530
他说他从没做一个大使
He said he was never an ambassador.

02:13.320 --> 02:15.030
不 不是一个大使
No, not an ambassador,

02:15.330 --> 02:16.750
我说"大使"
The Ambassador.

02:17.050 --> 02:19.570
我曾在大使宾馆的服务台工作
I was concierge at the Ambassador Hotel.

02:20.540 --> 02:22.880
我可以发誓 他曾在那干过几个月
I could've sworn he worked there for a few months.

02:25.320 --> 02:26.580
谁知道呢 对吗
Who the hell knows, huh?

02:26.700 --> 02:28.190
我经常磕药
I was high half the time.

02:28.580 --> 02:30.150
这也是我被炒的原因
Kind of why I got fired.

02:30.940 --> 02:32.360
是我在这儿的原因
Kind of why I'm in here.

02:32.370 --> 02:33.810
他在尼斯做什么?
What was he up to in Nice?

02:34.290 --> 02:35.390
怎么?
What?

02:35.400 --> 02:36.800
你要出书吗
You writing a book?

02:37.450 --> 02:39.390
我们3点13走 还有三小时又
We're leaving at 3:13 that gives us three hours

02:39.400 --> 02:41.890
41分钟 但我们还没办法进禁入区
41 minutes. And we still don't have a way into no-man's-land.

02:41.900 --> 02:42.510
我会搞定的
l'll take care of that.

02:42.520 --> 02:44.870
-只是我得先查探一下 -那监狱围栏呢?
I just need to check it out first. And the fence?

02:44.880 --> 02:46.480
你那个掘墓人朋友只洒过一次药水
Your grave digger friends only sprayed the thing once,

02:46.490 --> 02:48.180
我可不希望今天我被上电刑
And I'd just assume not get electrocuted today.

02:48.190 --> 02:50.380
苏克雷多洒一次会让我更有安心点吗 是的
Would I feel better if Sucre had sprayed the fence again? Yes.

02:50.390 --> 02:52.400
这可能吗 不
Is that an option? No.

02:52.590 --> 02:54.660
除非他又有进来的理由
Unless he had another reason to be there.

02:54.960 --> 02:55.530
你要做什么?
What are you going to do?

02:55.540 --> 02:57.630
杀个人好让他进来洒药水?
Kill someone to get more spray on the fence?

02:57.790 --> 03:00.310
我倒想杀了你 如果这能帮我们逃出去的话
I'd think about killing you if it helped us get out of here today.

03:00.920 --> 03:02.520
知道什么能帮我们逃出去吗
You know what'll help us get out of here?

03:02.530 --> 03:03.530
一把梯子
A ladder.

03:03.730 --> 03:04.640
迈克
Michael

03:05.560 --> 03:07.680
我们逃出去后要去哪儿?
where are we gonna go once we get through that fence?

03:08.950 --> 03:10.300
去弄把梯子来
Just get me a ladder.

03:15.070 --> 03:16.490
这张吊床比以前那个短
This hammock's shorter than the last one.

03:16.500 --> 03:18.110
那我们得弄点别的东西来接长它
Well, we might need something to extend it.

03:18.120 --> 03:19.870
好了 我来想办法
All right, I'll take care of it.

03:20.980 --> 03:22.550
我从没去过尼斯
I've never been to Nice.

03:22.900 --> 03:24.290
听说那儿很美
I hear it's beautiful.

03:24.860 --> 03:25.800
我怎么知道
I wouldn't know.

03:25.810 --> 03:27.610
我不管这个人是不是认识你
I don't care if this guy knows you or not.

03:27.620 --> 03:28.780
我在意的是
But what I do care about is

03:28.790 --> 03:31.420
他很明显一直在盯着你
his apparent fixation with watching you at all times.

03:31.940 --> 03:33.920
斯科菲尔德有访客
Scofield. Get a visita.

03:34.120 --> 03:35.540
我们很快就会出去了
We'll be out of here soon enough.

03:35.550 --> 03:36.680
他不是问题
He won't be a problem.

03:37.720 --> 03:39.960
斯科菲尔德有访客
Scofield, you have a visitor.

03:46.950 --> 03:48.270
伙计 看看这个
Hey, buddy, check it out.

03:48.280 --> 03:49.900
你们国家有玩骰子吗
Do they roll bones in your country?

03:49.930 --> 03:51.580
到我房间来 我教你
Come to my cell, I'll teach you.

03:52.420 --> 03:55.290
你要我去你牢房玩骰子?
You want me to come back to your cell and"roll bones"?

03:55.970 --> 03:57.230
真友好啊
Real subtle.

03:57.250 --> 03:58.370
很好玩的
Hardy har-har.

03:58.720 --> 04:00.260
是啊是啊 很有趣
Yeah, yeah, yeah, it's hilarious.

04:00.270 --> 04:01.180
告诉我
Tell me,

04:01.340 --> 04:03.640
你对这里所有没衣服穿的人都这么友好吗
are you this friendly with all the shirtless guys in Sona?

04:03.890 --> 04:05.080
我昨天给了你吃的
I gave you food yesterday.

04:05.090 --> 04:06.850
我给了你睡觉的地方
I gave you a place to sleep.

04:06.860 --> 04:07.930
我很好奇原因
I wonder why.

04:08.770 --> 04:09.500
你该死的有什么毛病?
What the hell is your problem?

04:09.510 --> 04:12.650
听着 我不想和你上床 明白吗
Look, I just don't want to have sex with you, okay?

04:15.060 --> 04:16.460
这很难接受吗
Is that so hard to believe?

04:26.140 --> 04:27.250
拿个盘子
Get a plate.

04:30.020 --> 04:31.910
要穿过禁入区
To make it across no-man's-land,

04:32.020 --> 04:34.130
我们必须对付两名守卫
we're going to have to disable two of the tower guards.

04:34.580 --> 04:35.770
一个已经可以搞定了
I've already taken care of one of them.

04:35.780 --> 04:37.680
另一个需要你的帮助
With the other one, we're going to need your help.

04:38.380 --> 04:39.890
每天中午1点到2点
Every day between 1:00 and 2:00,

04:39.900 --> 04:40.510
是他的午休时间
he takes his lunch break.

04:40.520 --> 04:41.870
他会喝一杯咖啡
He gets a cup of coffee.

04:41.990 --> 04:45.050
你得找出放杯子的地方 下点药进去
You need to find out where and put something in that cup.

04:45.060 --> 04:46.920
确保我们越狱时他意识不清
Make sure he's unconscious during the escape.

04:46.930 --> 04:48.950
你让我在三个小时之内把这事搞定?
You're dropping this on me with three hours to go?

04:49.660 --> 04:51.910
-我不知道该说什么 -3点13?
I don't know what to tell you. 3:13?

04:52.020 --> 04:53.600
3点13开始动手
3:13 is when it starts.

04:53.830 --> 04:55.640
我们3点25抵达海滩
We'll be on the beach by 3:25.

04:55.650 --> 04:56.830
在大白天
In broad daylight.

04:56.840 --> 04:58.620
组织仍以为我们是在今晚9点
The Company still thinks we're doing this at 9:00

04:58.630 --> 04:59.160
开始行动 对吗
tonight, right?

04:59.170 --> 05:01.530
听着 我不能再骗这些人了迈克
Listen, I can't lie to these people anymore, Michael.

05:01.540 --> 05:03.500
我们需要时间查看人质移交点
We need time to survey the transfer site,

05:03.510 --> 05:05.630
看看有没有办法把莎拉和LJ救出来
to figure out if we can get LJ and Sara out of there

05:05.640 --> 05:07.130
以防他们玩阴的
in case they try something.

05:08.230 --> 05:10.160
-你弄到枪了? -是的 我弄到了
You got the gun? Yeah, I got the gun.

05:12.560 --> 05:14.100
LJ怎么样? 莎拉呢?
How's LJ? How's Sara?

05:14.480 --> 05:15.430
他们没事
They're fine.

05:15.840 --> 05:17.190
照片呢?
What about the pictures?

05:18.070 --> 05:19.360
我拿不到照片
I can't get pictures.

05:19.840 --> 05:20.580
我要照片 林肯
I need them, Linc.

05:20.590 --> 05:22.140
我拿不到照片
I can't get the pictures.

05:22.150 --> 05:23.370
我们怎么肯定他们还活着?
How do we know they're still alive?

05:23.380 --> 05:24.970
他们是我愿做这事的唯一原因啊
They're the only reason I'm doing this.

05:24.980 --> 05:25.820
苏珊说他们很好
Susan says they're fine.

05:25.830 --> 05:27.870
-相信她吧 -你总是告诉我
Just trust her. You're the one who's always telling me

05:27.880 --> 05:28.810
不能相信任何人
we can't trust anybody.

05:28.820 --> 05:31.140
现在你 你却为这个人做担保?
Now you're you're vouching for this person?

05:31.150 --> 05:33.000
没时间了
There isn't enough time.

05:35.140 --> 05:38.840
听着 如果我在今天中午2:30之前
Listen, if I don't see pictures of LJ and Sara by 2:30

05:38.850 --> 05:40.120
看不到LJ和莎拉的照片
this afternoon,

05:41.360 --> 05:42.720
我哪里都不会去
I'm not going anywhere.

