06:33.000 --> 06:35.310
我找不到美国产的奶酪
Can't seem to find American cheese down here.

06:35.320 --> 06:36.930
希望你喜欢阿萨德产的
I hope you like Asadero.

06:37.630 --> 06:39.520
没事 很好
Yeah. It's perfect.

06:40.720 --> 06:43.910
几年前 我在摩苏尔打仗
A couple of years ago, I was serving in Mosul.

06:45.160 --> 06:46.920
我被敌人俘虏了
And I was taken prisoner.

06:47.580 --> 06:48.600
过了几个漫长的晚上后
A few nights later,

06:48.610 --> 06:52.160
我听到了美军直升机的声音
I could hear the sound of U.S. Army helicopters.

06:52.410 --> 06:53.900
越来越近
Two clicks and closing.

06:55.940 --> 06:57.350
我的手当时是被绑着的
My hands were still tied behind my back,

06:57.360 --> 06:58.920
但我还是逃了
and I I ran.

06:59.340 --> 07:00.960
我当时没有想到
It didn't occur to me

07:01.070 --> 07:03.050
如果这是一次营救任务
that if this was a rescue mission,

07:03.480 --> 07:05.690
那么敌人也会听到直升机声音的
my captors could hear the choppers.

07:06.800 --> 07:07.710
我没有想到
It didn't occur to me

07:07.720 --> 07:10.640
这次的任务其实是人质交换
that this was actually a hostage exchange,

07:12.330 --> 07:13.320
但是
and that

07:13.670 --> 07:16.320
我的逃跑会被视为
jumping would be viewed

07:16.660 --> 07:18.420
敌对行为
as a hostile act.

07:21.440 --> 07:23.420
我很快又被抓起来了
I got recaptured immediately.

07:24.750 --> 07:26.410
6名突击队员死于
Six Rangers died

07:27.050 --> 07:28.180
枪战
in the firefight.

07:30.320 --> 07:32.020
接下来的三个星期
And for the next three weeks

07:39.100 --> 07:40.360
这么说吧
Let's just say

07:41.640 --> 07:42.860
人都是畜牲
men are pigs.

07:47.810 --> 07:49.070
我们丑话说在前头
Let's be clear.

07:50.760 --> 07:52.690
这是一次交换
This is an exchange.

07:53.660 --> 07:55.410
不要逞能
If you don't try to be a hero,

07:55.480 --> 07:57.240
这样你和你爸爸都不会有事
you and your father will be okay.

07:58.070 --> 07:59.960
-明白了吗? -明白
Okay? Okay.

08:00.300 --> 08:01.290
很好
Good.

08:05.270 --> 08:06.200
吃吧
Eat.

08:10.670 --> 08:13.240
诺曼? 诺曼?
Norman? Norman?

08:13.310 --> 08:14.010
你该知道
As you can imagine,

08:14.020 --> 08:15.300
他喜欢勒齐
he prefers Lechero.

08:15.310 --> 08:16.340
诺曼?
Norman?

08:16.730 --> 08:19.140
他不管你交不交保护费都会杀了你
He kills you before or after he does your taxes.

08:21.000 --> 08:23.570
他杀你可不需要理由
He Kills you when he pleases.

08:23.950 --> 08:25.390
我口渴了
I'm feeling thirsty.

08:25.420 --> 08:27.620
你为什么不帮我们拿点喝的 小子
Why don't you go fix us something to drink, boy?

08:27.630 --> 08:29.270
也许你还没接到通知
Maybe you ain't got the memorandum,

08:29.280 --> 08:30.860
我已经被提升了
but I've been promoted.

08:31.020 --> 08:32.140
小子
Boy.

08:35.730 --> 08:36.910
你刚才对我说什么?
What did you say to me?

08:37.860 --> 08:38.940
有什么事吗
What's the problem?

08:39.960 --> 08:41.600
有人打肿脸充胖子
Stumpy herand his mouth.

08:41.610 --> 08:42.620
就是这个问题
That's the problem.

08:42.630 --> 08:44.340
我现在就要和他出去把问题解决
I'm calling him out right now

08:44.730 --> 08:47.110
我会和他谈谈 你出去
I'll talk to him. Leave.

08:50.410 --> 08:50.990
这事没完
This isn't over.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.170
都出去
Leave

08:58.830 --> 08:59.760
我们只是
We was just, uh

08:59.770 --> 09:00.850
不 不
No, no, no.

09:01.190 --> 09:02.430
你欠我个情
The favor you owe me

09:02.440 --> 09:03.890
你发现了什么吗
What have you found out?

09:03.960 --> 09:05.810
这种事情是要时间的
A thing like this takes time.

09:05.920 --> 09:08.380
我不可能走到他面前直接问
I can't just walk up to them and say,"Hey, whoever's been

09:08.390 --> 09:10.640
谁背叛了勒齐请举手
betraying Lechero, raise your hand."You know?

09:10.920 --> 09:12.960
我让你在这里当我的耳线
I asked you to be my ears in this prison,

09:12.970 --> 09:14.340
你什么料都收不到?
and you hear nothing?

09:14.350 --> 09:16.450
我只知道每一次我坐下来准备
All I know is every time I try and sit down and begin

09:16.460 --> 09:19.230
了解点什么的时候 萨米总是扯开话题
sussing things out, Sammy always changes the subject.

09:19.240 --> 09:20.860
我不是说他就是叛徒 但
Not that I'm saying he's the guy, but

09:20.870 --> 09:23.390
我不想听你的理论
I don't want to hear your theories.

09:24.090 --> 09:25.390
我要的是结论
I want results.

09:45.180 --> 09:46.350
情况还好吗
Is everything okay?

09:46.510 --> 09:48.230
-詹姆斯怎么样? -是的 他很好
Is James all right? Yeah, he's fine.

09:49.320 --> 09:50.220
这东西哪里来的?
Where is this from?

09:51.620 --> 09:53.110
乌瑞伯 在波德格的
Uribe's, the roadside

09:53.120 --> 09:54.910
路边 就几公里远
Bodega a few kilometers away.

09:54.920 --> 09:56.920
如果我想你去辩认一个警卫
If I needed you to ID a specific guard

09:56.920 --> 09:58.320
哨塔的警卫 你能做得到吗?
a tower guard could you do it?

09:59.320 --> 10:00.820
我只是不想被抓起来
I just don't want to get busted.

10:00.820 --> 10:01.820
到底能不能做到?
Could you do it or not?

10:02.320 --> 10:03.220
可以
Yes.

10:07.920 --> 10:09.120
-林肯? -是的
Lincoln? Yeah.

10:09.320 --> 10:10.920
-什么事? -我需要点帮助
What is it? I need something.

10:38.220 --> 10:39.210
蒂博格也干不了什么坏事的 老兄
Teodoro's harmless, man.

10:39.220 --> 10:41.820
-他是一个 小丑 -一个该死的小丑
He's a he's clown. He's a dead clown.

10:48.220 --> 10:49.610
老兄 我不会到处说
Hey, man, I wasn't going to say anything,

10:49.620 --> 10:52.120
但是 昨晚
but, uh, last night,

10:53.220 --> 10:55.820
我在找扑克的时候 你猜怎么着
I was looking for my playing cards and guess what?

10:57.520 --> 10:58.520
我发现了这个
I found these.

10:59.020 --> 11:00.120
你竟然瞒着我
You're holding out on me.

11:00.920 --> 11:01.810
喜欢都拿去
Take'em.

11:01.820 --> 11:02.920
口感很差
They taste nasty.

11:03.220 --> 11:06.120
老兄 你找不到再好的雪茄了
Man, you cannot get a better cigar than this.

11:06.220 --> 11:08.220
你从谁那里拿的? 奥古斯特?
Where'd you get these? Augusto?

11:09.020 --> 11:10.010
他要给我 我也阻止不了
I can't make him stop sending them in to me,

11:10.020 --> 11:12.020
不过我可不是他的人 你明白吗?
but I don't work for him, you understand?

11:14.320 --> 11:15.320
你确定不介意?
You sure you don't mind?

11:49.920 --> 11:51.720
我在这附近
I was in the neighborhood.

11:56.220 --> 11:57.920
我那么老远过来探望我?
You came all this way to visit?

11:58.520 --> 11:59.920
我来是想把你弄出来
I came to get you out of here.

12:00.420 --> 12:02.110
我能在48小时之后把你转去Schaum
I can have you in Schaum Correctional Facility

12:02.120 --> 12:03.320
的监禁中心
in 48 hours.

12:04.420 --> 12:05.520
在圣路易斯
In St. Louis.

12:05.920 --> 12:07.410
苏林斯希望把你关在相对戒备森严的地方
Sullins wanted a medium security,

12:07.420 --> 12:09.420
但我说服了他
but, uh, talked him down.

12:09.820 --> 12:11.420
他给我什么的方案作为交易?
What sort of deal is he getting me?

12:11.620 --> 12:13.020
25年?
25 years?

12:13.320 --> 12:14.320
终身监禁?
Life?

12:14.420 --> 12:16.310
上级给予我们很大的让步
The director's giving us a lot of latitude

12:16.320 --> 12:18.210
以此交换你在政府对林肯·布鲁斯
in exchange for testimony against the government

12:18.220 --> 12:19.820
这次阴谋事件上的证词
in the Lincoln Burrows conspiracy.

12:20.720 --> 12:21.720
那么
So

12:23.120 --> 12:24.620
8年怎么样?
how does eight years sound?

12:26.220 --> 12:27.920
苏林斯安排好
Soon as Sullins finishes up,

12:27.920 --> 12:29.320
我们准备好车
we can have a van ready

12:30.020 --> 12:31.220
我不接受
I don't think so.

12:32.020 --> 12:33.020
什么?
What?

12:33.720 --> 12:35.310
谢谢你们的努力
I appreciate the effort,

12:35.320 --> 12:39.320
你的努力 但是 我不能忍受被关押8年
your effort, but, um, I can't do eight years.

12:39.520 --> 12:41.020
你现在最起码要坐10年
You're doing ten now.

12:42.620 --> 12:44.720
政府现在需要你做点事
The government is calling in some favors.

12:44.720 --> 12:47.310
一旦你回到美国 如果你不合作
Once you're in the U.S., if you don't cooperate,

12:47.320 --> 12:48.410
他们会起诉你所有的犯罪行为
they're going to charge you with everything.

12:48.420 --> 12:50.320
那可包括多起谋杀案的
That's multiple homicide counts.

12:55.120 --> 12:56.310
你不答应这交易
Without this deal,

12:56.320 --> 12:58.620
你一辈子都要在牢里了
you are gonna be in prison for the rest of your life.

13:01.220 --> 13:02.720
谢谢你们的努力
I appreciate the effort,

13:03.320 --> 13:04.420
你的努力
your effort.

13:05.420 --> 13:06.420
但我不能
But I can't.

13:07.920 --> 13:08.920
阿历克斯
Alex.

13:12.800 --> 13:14.300
我们行动的时候 如果
While we're getting out of here, and

13:16.100 --> 13:17.500
如果我不能成功
if I don't make it,

13:18.300 --> 13:20.600
你能答应我一定将这个给我女朋友吗
will you make sure this gets to my girlfriend?

13:23.600 --> 13:24.700
好的
All right.

13:28.400 --> 13:31.490
你知道的 如果你 我也可以帮你这么做
You know, uh I could do the same for you.

13:31.500 --> 13:33.000
把这个绑紧了
Tie an anchor bend there.

13:34.800 --> 13:35.490
我只是提一下
I was just offering.

13:35.500 --> 13:37.600
你知道吗 如果我逃不出去
You know what, if I'm the one who doesn't make it,

13:37.700 --> 13:39.200
如果你真心想帮我
and you really want to do me a favor,

13:39.200 --> 13:40.800
就是坚持与对方的谈判
just hold up your end of the bargain.

13:42.500 --> 13:43.900
我会尽我所能的
I'll do everything I can.

13:44.000 --> 13:45.100
我希望那是真的
I hope that's true.

13:46.300 --> 13:47.500
那个结是从哪来的?
How's that knot coming?

13:49.300 --> 13:50.400
你看
There.

13:51.800 --> 13:53.200
我合格了吗?
Did I pass your test?

13:54.200 --> 13:55.800
我告诉过你我是个渔民
I told you I'm a fisherman.

13:58.000 --> 13:58.790
进展如何?
Where are we?

13:58.800 --> 14:00.890
我发现了一个能让我们到达禁入区的牢房
I found a cell that'll get us into no-man's-land.

14:00.900 --> 14:03.090
比从我的旧牢房到达围墙要远一些
It's a longer run to the fence than my old one,

14:03.100 --> 14:04.300
但必须得从那走
but it's gonna have to do.

14:04.500 --> 14:06.000
哪一间? 谁住那?
Which one? Who liveshere?

14:06.600 --> 14:08.700
帕波乔还有萨米
Papo, Cheo and Sammy.

14:09.200 --> 14:10.600
听着 我知道你在想什么
Look, I know what you're thinking,

14:10.700 --> 14:12.390
但这是第二层唯一另一间
but it's the only other cell on the second floor

14:12.400 --> 14:14.990
可以不被岗哨发现直达围墙的牢房
with a direct line to the fence, where we won't be seen

14:15.000 --> 14:16.590
我们怎么保证
the other tower guards. And how do we

14:16.600 --> 14:17.990
他们不会在那出现?
guarantee that they won't be there?

14:18.000 --> 14:19.990
到两点时 每个人都会到操场
By 2:00, everyone should be out in the courtyard

14:20.000 --> 14:21.800
观看午餐足球比赛
for the lunchtime soccer game.

14:23.400 --> 14:25.100
你确信那还没开始?
You sure it hasn't started already?

14:33.900 --> 14:36.600
某人不经过决斗来解决问题
Someone went outside the ring to settle a dispute.

14:38.200 --> 14:40.990
现在 谁破坏了这个规矩
Now, anyone who affronts our justice system

14:41.000 --> 14:43.100
谁就要被依此受惩罚
in this way must be punished.

14:43.800 --> 14:46.500
现在 我知道那懦夫不敢吭声
Now, I know the coward won't come forward.

14:46.800 --> 14:50.000
但如果有人有关于此事的信息
But if anyone has information about this shameful act,

14:51.100 --> 14:52.600
告诉我
I demand to know.

15:02.100 --> 15:03.790
-走吧 穆多 -干吗?
Let's go, Menudo. Why?

15:03.800 --> 15:05.900
勒齐想找你 快走
Lechero wants you. Move your ass.

15:07.800 --> 15:09.690
每天我看你在院子里呆着
Now, every day I see you out in the yard,

15:09.700 --> 15:10.790
玩你的美国运动
you play your American sports

15:10.800 --> 15:12.090
穿着你的美国球衣
and wear your American clothes.

15:12.100 --> 15:13.090
我觉得从你来之后
I don't think I've heard you

15:13.100 --> 15:15.000
没你说过一句西班牙语
speak one word of Spanish since you've been here.

15:15.100 --> 15:17.000
我想练习英文
I like to practice my English.

15:17.100 --> 15:18.300
没什么不好
And why shouldn't you?

15:19.400 --> 15:20.800
美国是个伟大的国家
America is a great nation.

15:21.900 --> 15:25.190
"一个不可分割的国家 自由与公正属于所有人"
"One nation, indivisible, with liberty and justice for all."

15:25.200 --> 15:26.100
没错吧?
Is that right?

15:26.600 --> 15:27.390
对
Yes.

15:27.400 --> 15:28.500
没错
Yes.

15:29.100 --> 15:30.500
对所有人都要公平
Justice for all.

15:31.000 --> 15:34.200
你我都一样
Justice for you and justice for me.

15:35.700 --> 15:37.300
而对
And justice for

15:37.600 --> 15:39.700
那个在院子里杀了布朗齐多的凶手也要公平
whoever killed that blanquito in the yard.

15:41.000 --> 15:43.300
我知道你为什么在那一言不发
Now, I know why you didn't say anything out there.

15:43.800 --> 15:46.690
但你每天都在那玩恶心的美国游戏
But you play your silly American games all day long,

15:46.700 --> 15:49.200
就在尸体被发现的楼梯前面
right in front of the stairs where the body was found.

15:51.000 --> 15:53.500
现在 如果你不告诉我你看到了什么
Now, if you don't tell me what you saw,

15:55.200 --> 15:56.900
会有你好看的
there will be consequences.

16:02.700 --> 16:06.100
我 我看到一个人走进楼梯间
Well, I-I saw one person go into the stairwell.

16:08.500 --> 16:12.100
好像一分钟之后 我听到争吵声
A-And then maybe a minute later, I heard an argument.

16:12.900 --> 16:14.700
你看到谁了?
Who did you see?

16:18.400 --> 16:20.100
那么在我们松开绳子后
So after we tie the cord off

16:21.700 --> 16:23.590
我们切断栏杆 打通窗户
we dig out the bar, we pop open the grate,

16:23.600 --> 16:24.690
然后我们就逃出去 没错吧迈克?
and we're, and we're down, right, Michael?

16:24.700 --> 16:25.790
有人想说说
Does anyone want to say anything

16:25.800 --> 16:27.500
我们刚看到的东西吗?
about what we just saw out there?

16:29.000 --> 16:29.890
说什么?
What is there to say?

16:29.900 --> 16:31.290
首先 一小时前
Well, for starters, an hour ago,

16:31.300 --> 16:32.590
你说也许我们得杀个人
you say maybe we should kill someone

16:32.600 --> 16:33.690
然后就有人被杀了
and then someone gets killed.

16:33.700 --> 16:35.290
我没说过 而那
I didn't say that, and this is exactly

16:35.300 --> 16:36.590
就是我们现在必须关注的
what we should be focusing on right now.

16:36.600 --> 16:37.890
让我们花几个小时
Let's spend a couple of hours worrying

16:37.900 --> 16:40.200
担心在这鬼地方的另一具尸体
about another dead body in this hellhole.

16:40.600 --> 16:41.700
你们要干吗?
What do you want?

16:42.500 --> 16:43.400
你们要干吗?
What are you doing?

16:43.500 --> 16:44.690
勒齐想见你
Lechero wants to see you.

16:44.700 --> 16:45.990
我什么信息都没有
I don't have any information.

16:46.000 --> 16:47.400
他不需要信息
He doesn't want information.

16:47.400 --> 16:48.700
他需要招供
He wants a confession.

16:57.300 --> 16:58.600
我什么都没做
I didn't do anything.

16:58.600 --> 17:00.000
他说的没错 他是无辜的
Listen to him; he's innocent.

17:01.500 --> 17:02.700
那你想招供?
You want to confess?

17:02.800 --> 17:04.400
那你来代替他啊
You can easily switch places.

17:09.000 --> 17:10.190
也许现在我们得开始担心
Maybe now we should start worrying

17:10.200 --> 17:11.900
那个真正的杀手了吧?
about who the real killer is, huh?

17:12.600 --> 17:14.590
是啊 但在这里
Yeah, but in this place,

17:14.600 --> 17:16.090
也许有一百个人在嫌疑名单上
there could be a hundred people on that list.

17:16.100 --> 17:17.790
除了我觉得在死者脖子底部
Except I'm thinking a single stab wound

17:17.800 --> 17:20.100
有个刀疤 而那伤口一看就是高手干的 阿历克斯
to the base of the neck looks pretty professional, Alex.

17:20.300 --> 17:21.690
我当时正有人探视 老兄
I was in visitation, Kojak.

17:21.700 --> 17:24.300
什么让你这么肯定惠斯勒没杀人?
And what makes you so sure that Whistler didn't do it?

17:24.300 --> 17:26.090
他可是与他有纠葛的人
He's the one that had the run-in with the guy.

17:26.100 --> 17:27.590
不可能 他不会为这事去冒险
No, he's got too much to lose.

17:27.600 --> 17:28.690
惠斯勒出局了 即使不是现在
Whistler's gone, and if not now,

17:28.700 --> 17:30.490
也快了 所以就剩我们俩
he probably will be soon, so it's you and me.

17:30.500 --> 17:31.800
没有所谓的我们俩
There's no you and me.

17:32.100 --> 17:33.500
我们不会丢下他逃走的
We're not leaving here without him.

17:33.800 --> 17:36.090
在两个小时内 我将要爬出窗户 翻过那围墙
In two hours, I'm going out that window and through that fence.

17:36.100 --> 17:37.890
是吗? 很好
Oh, yeah? Yeah, that's right.

17:37.900 --> 17:39.190
你想跑哪去 阿历克斯?
And where are you going to go to, Alex?

17:39.200 --> 17:40.290
哪都去不了
Anywhere but here.

17:40.300 --> 17:41.700
只有一条路能出去
There's only one road out,

17:41.900 --> 17:43.990
树林里有24小时不间断巡逻
and the jungle is under constant patrol by police 24-7,

17:44.000 --> 17:46.100
那我再问一次 你想跑哪去阿历克斯?
so, again, where are you going to go to, Alex?

17:46.100 --> 17:48.200
3点13分 我会离开的
3:13, I'm gone.

17:54.100 --> 17:56.000
我说过我对此一无所知
I told you I know nothing about this.

17:56.400 --> 17:57.600
我不应该
I shouldn't

17:57.900 --> 17:59.090
我不该被带这来
I shouldn't be here.

17:59.100 --> 18:01.700
我能向你保证 我没杀人
I can promise you I, I did not kill that man.

18:01.700 --> 18:03.500
有人看到你走下楼梯
Someone saw you go down the staircase.

18:03.700 --> 18:05.900
楼梯 还有什么证据吗?
Stai.. is there any other proof?

18:06.200 --> 18:07.500
我的人会找到证据的
My men will find something.

18:07.600 --> 18:09.200
那你看到我身上有凶器吗?
Well, do you see a weapon on me?

18:09.200 --> 18:11.090
我才不期望能在你身上看到凶器
I didn't expect to see a weapon on you.

18:11.100 --> 18:12.890
那他们怎么不去找那个?
Well, w-why don't they look for that?

18:12.900 --> 18:14.590
找到凶器 就找到了真正的杀手
You find that, you'll find the real killer.

18:14.600 --> 18:16.490
或者也许他们找到了你埋凶器的地方
Or maybe they find where you planted it.

18:16.500 --> 18:17.990
你是说我在栽赃?
So, what, I'm framing someone?

18:18.000 --> 18:19.190
那你想过
Well, did it ever occur to you

18:19.200 --> 18:21.590
也许有人在设计陷害我? 谁会这样做?
that someone might be framing me? Who would bother?

18:21.600 --> 18:22.690
你知道我被关在这的原因
You know the reason I'm here.

18:22.700 --> 18:23.890
你知道我有强大的敌人
You know I have powerful enemies.

18:23.900 --> 18:26.200
你认为我的判断会被市长的朋友左右吗?
You think my judgment is swayed by the mayor's friends?

18:26.400 --> 18:27.900
坐下吧
Sit your ass down.

18:29.000 --> 18:30.200
当我13岁时
When I was 13,

18:32.400 --> 18:34.500
我妈妈在一个有钱人家当仆人
my mother worked for a wealthy man as a maid

18:35.600 --> 18:36.900
直到有一天
until one day

18:38.500 --> 18:40.300
她一个人呆在房子里
she was alone in the house

18:42.200 --> 18:43.600
和他待在一起
with him and he

18:49.100 --> 18:50.700
所有人都知道他干了什么
Everybody knew what he did,

18:53.600 --> 18:55.300
但是由于他是富人
but because he was rich

18:55.600 --> 18:57.500
而我们是移民
and we were immigrants,

18:58.700 --> 19:00.800
警察连报案都不接受
the police wouldn't even take a report.

19:03.000 --> 19:05.400
然后 一周之后
So, a week later,

19:05.500 --> 19:07.500
为了接近他
to gain access through his gates,

19:08.500 --> 19:11.700
我装扮成送牛奶的——一个勒齐
I dressed as a milkman a Lechero

19:12.800 --> 19:16.300
我确保 他得到其应有的惩罚
and I made sure that fair punishment was rendered.

19:17.500 --> 19:19.900
现在你来说说我会怎么偏袒富人
Now you want to tell me how I favor the rich.

19:22.800 --> 19:26.500
我知道这里的规矩 我也尊重它
I understand the rules here, and I respect them.

19:27.800 --> 19:29.600
为什么这么急着下结论?
But why the rush to judgment?

19:30.200 --> 19:32.790
有哪个条款规定你必须在
Is there a rule saying you must convict a suspect

19:32.800 --> 19:34.000
10分钟内找到嫌疑犯吗
within ten minutes?

19:37.800 --> 19:38.800
没有
No.

19:43.600 --> 19:45.100
我们有大把时间慢慢研究
We have all the time in the world.

19:47.500 --> 19:48.400
谢谢你
Thank you.

19:48.800 --> 19:50.700
当然 现在我哪也不会去
Now, obviously, I'm not going anywhere.

19:50.700 --> 19:52.900
如果你还想聊聊 我就在我的单间里
If you need to talk again, I'm gonna be in my cell.

19:53.000 --> 19:53.900
不用了
No.

19:54.300 --> 19:56.500
你只能坐在这把椅子上
You'll be right here in this chair.

20:12.650 --> 20:14.140
你到底想要做什么?
What the hell do you want?

20:14.150 --> 20:15.150
我不喜欢你
I don't like you.

20:16.150 --> 20:18.050
当然也没有尊重你
I certainly don't respect you.

20:18.350 --> 20:19.640
够了 你在伤害我的感觉
Stop. You're hurting my feelings.

20:19.650 --> 20:21.740
你也知道你能干什么
I've seen at you're capable of,

20:21.750 --> 20:22.950
但我不得不承认
but I got to say

20:22.950 --> 20:24.650
我从来没想过你会杀人
I never pegged you as a murderer.

20:25.950 --> 20:27.450
你认为是我杀了帝格?
You think I killed Tyge?

20:27.950 --> 20:31.540
我今早在院子里看见你们俩了
I saw the two of you in the courtyard this morning.

20:31.550 --> 20:32.840
我只是想跟他交朋友
I was trying to be Nice to him.

20:32.850 --> 20:33.940
是他先和我过不去的
He started with me.

20:33.950 --> 20:35.450
如果不是你杀的 那会是谁?
Well, if you didn't kill him, who did?

20:35.950 --> 20:36.650
不是我
Not me.

20:36.650 --> 20:37.850
别嘴硬了 布拉德
Come on, Brad.

20:38.350 --> 20:39.850
除了你以为谁还会想要他的小命?
Who wanted him dead besides you?

20:39.850 --> 20:41.450
你当真以为是我杀了那个呆瓜?
You really think I killed that frog?

20:41.750 --> 20:44.050
我拿着枪口对着你多少次了?
How many times have I had you at gunpoint?

20:44.350 --> 20:46.150
你以为我不想开枪?
You think I didn't want to pull that trigger?

20:50.350 --> 20:50.950
天啊
Hell

20:52.650 --> 20:54.450
我连自杀都没办法
I can't even kill myself.

21:04.550 --> 21:07.450
你知道有谁看见惠斯勒从这楼梯下去吗?
Hey, you seen anyone see Whistler go down the stairway?

21:07.750 --> 21:09.250
我们才出来1分钟
We only been out here a minute.

21:09.350 --> 21:10.540
那么快点了
Well, hurry up, then.

21:10.550 --> 21:11.950
惠斯勒死的越早
The sooner Whistler dies,

21:12.750 --> 21:14.650
那我就能越早给你鸡爪
the sooner I can give you the chicken foot,

21:14.850 --> 21:17.040
也许你更喜欢给我鸡爪
or if you prefer, you can give me the chicken foot

21:17.050 --> 21:19.150
像个男人一样试试
you know, try and go out like a man.

21:19.850 --> 21:22.550
随便选 你今天得和我决斗
Either way, you're getting in the ring with me today.

21:32.350 --> 21:35.650
Zylafol 用来麻醉狗的
Zylafol. It's used to anesthetize dogs.

21:35.650 --> 21:37.950
2滴 守卫就会在一个小时内昏迷
Two drops, and the guard should be out within an hour.

21:39.150 --> 21:41.250
我还以为惠斯勒的女朋友会参与行动
I was expecting Whistler's girlfriend to join you.

21:41.350 --> 21:43.040
她在哪 转角的车里?
Where is she? Around the corner in the car?

21:43.050 --> 21:44.150
她来找过我
She came to me.

21:44.550 --> 21:45.740
我不介意她帮助你
I don't mind that she's helping you.

21:45.750 --> 21:47.350
我介意的是你对我保密
I mind that you kept it from me.

21:47.950 --> 21:49.040
有什么关系呢
